ecl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/93d4ae6635c0c755c9f7368f9b99483d4557b7a6/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1771-L1771","name":"List.groupBy","line":1771,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.groupBy","doc":"`O(|l|)`. `splitBy R l` splits `l` into chains of elements\nsuch that adjacent elements are related by `R`.\n\n* `splitBy (·==·) [1, 1, 2, 2, 2, 3, 2] = [[1, 1], [2, 2, 2], [3], [2]]`\n* `splitBy (·<·) [1, 2, 5, 4, 5, 1, 4] = [[1, 2, 5], [4, 5], [1, 4]]`\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.groupBy\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">groupBy</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(R : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span>)</span></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/93d4ae6635c0c755c9f7368f9b99483d4557b7a6/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1765-L1769","name":"List.splitBy.loop","line":1765,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.splitBy.loop","doc":"The arguments of `splitBy.loop l ag g gs` represent the following:\n\n- `l : List α` are the elements which we still need to split.\n- `ag : α` is the previous element for which a comparison was performed.\n- `g : List α` is the group currently being assembled, in **reverse order**.\n- `gs : List (List α)` is all of the groups that have been completed, in **reverse order**.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.splitBy.loop\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">splitBy</span>.<span class=\"name\">loop</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(R : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span>)</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span>)</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/93d4ae6635c0c755c9f7368f9b99483d4557b7a6/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1746-L1769","name":"List.splitBy","line":1746,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.splitBy","doc":"`O(|l|)`. `splitBy R l` splits `l` into chains of elements\nsuch that adjacent elements are related by `R`.\n\n* `splitBy (·==·) [1, 1, 2, 2, 2, 3, 2] = [[1, 1], [2, 2, 2], [3], [2]]`\n* `splitBy (·<·) [1, 2, 5, 4, 5, 1, 4] = [[1, 2, 5], [4, 5], [1, 4]]`\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.splitBy\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">splitBy</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(R : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span>)</span></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/93d4ae6635c0c755c9f7368f9b99483d4557b7a6/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1738-L1742","name":"List.span.loop","line":1738,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.span.loop","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.span.loop\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">span</span>.<span class=\"name\">loop</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(p : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/93d4ae6635c0c755c9f7368f9b99483d4557b7a6/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1727-L1742","name":"List.span","line":1727,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.span","doc":"`O(|l|)`. `span p l` splits the list `l` into two parts, where the first part\ncontains the longest initial segment for which `p` returns true\nand the second part is everything else.\n\n* `span (· > 5) [6, 8, 9, 5, 2, 9] = ([6, 8, 9], [5, 2, 9])`\n* `span (· > 10) [6, 8, 9, 5, 2, 9] = ([], [6, 8, 9, 5, 2, 9])`\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.span\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">span</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(p : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(as : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/93d4ae6635c0c755c9f7368f9b99483d4557b7a6/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1719-L1723","name":"List.eraseReps.loop","line":1719,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.eraseReps.loop","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.eraseReps.loop\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">eraseReps</span>.<span class=\"name\">loop</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#BEq\">BEq</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/93d4ae6635c0c755c9f7368f9b99483d4557b7a6/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1711-L1723","name":"List.eraseReps","line":1711,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.eraseReps","doc":"`O(|l|)`. Erase repeated adjacent elements. Keeps the first occurrence of each run.\n* `eraseReps [1, 3, 2, 2, 2, 3, 5] = [1, 3, 2, 3, 5]`\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.eraseReps\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">eraseReps</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#BEq\">BEq</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/93d4ae6635c0c755c9f7368f9b99483d4557b7a6/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1703-L1707","name":"List.eraseDups.loop","line":1703,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.eraseDups.loop","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.eraseDups.loop\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">eraseDups</span>.<span class=\"name\">loop</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#BEq\">BEq</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"f