"name\">dropLast_nil</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.nil\">[</a><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.nil\">]</a>.<a href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.dropLast\">dropLast</a></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.nil\">[</a><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.nil\">]</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/93d4ae6635c0c755c9f7368f9b99483d4557b7a6/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L893-L902","name":"List.dropLast","line":893,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.dropLast","doc":"Removes the last element of the list.\n* `dropLast [] = []`\n* `dropLast [a] = []`\n* `dropLast [a, b, c] = [a, b]`\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.dropLast\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">dropLast</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/93d4ae6635c0c755c9f7368f9b99483d4557b7a6/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L884-L889","name":"List.partition.loop","line":884,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.partition.loop","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.partition.loop\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">partition</span>.<span class=\"name\">loop</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(p : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/93d4ae6635c0c755c9f7368f9b99483d4557b7a6/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L871-L889","name":"List.partition","line":871,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.partition","doc":"`O(|l|)`. `partition p l` calls `p` on each element of `l`, partitioning the list into two lists\n`(l_true, l_false)` where `l_true` has the elements where `p` was true\nand `l_false` has the elements where `p` is false.\n`partition p l = (filter p l, filter (not ∘ p) l)`, but it is slightly more efficient\nsince it only has to do one pass over the list.\n```\npartition (· > 2) [1, 2, 5, 2, 7, 7] = ([5, 7, 7], [1, 2, 2])\n```\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.partition\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">partition</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(p : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(as : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/93d4ae6635c0c755c9f7368f9b99483d4557b7a6/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L867-L867","name":"List.dropWhile_nil","line":867,"kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.dropWhile_nil","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.dropWhile_nil\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">dropWhile_nil</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{p : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.dropWhile\">dropWhile</a> <span class=\"fn\">p</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.nil\">[</a><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.nil\">]</a></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.nil\">[</a><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.nil\">]</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/93d4ae6635c0c755c9f7368f9b99483d4557b7a6/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L854-L865","name":"List.dropWhile","line":854,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.dropWhile","doc":"`O(|l|)`. `dropWhile p l` removes elements from the list until it finds the first element\nfor which `p` returns false; this element and everything after it is returned.\n```\ndropWhile (· < 4) [1, 3, 2, 4, 2, 7, 4] = [4, 2, 7, 4]\n```\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.dropWhile\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">dropWhile</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(p : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/93d4ae6635c0c755c9f7368f9b99483d4557b7a6/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L850-L850","name":"List.takeWhile_nil","line":850,"kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.takeWhile_nil","doc":""},"header":"<